The targets were cut into size of 1.5 x 1.5 cm2 each
and were pasted on rectangular Al target holders
having concentric holes of 1.2 cm diam.

E=165 MeV and E=132 MeV and 40 nA
kept between two successive 165Ho targets that served
as catchers as well as energy degraders, wherever
